Reasoning: The paper deals with the design and optimization of LDPC codes for wireless communication systems, which falls under the scope of information theory (cs.IT) and communication (cs.COMM). The use of LDPC codes in wireless networks also involves network infrastructure (cs.NI) and system integration (cs.SI). Additionally, the proposed variable node matched mapping (VNMM) scheme and hierarchical extrinsic information transfer (EXIT) algorithm may involve data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
